Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.73,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.34,0:00:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.69,0:00:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.76,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.43,0:00:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.87,0:00:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.58,0:00:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.95,0:01:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.91,0:01:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.47,0:01:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦妳了立花中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.45,0:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠著妳收集的資料\N地球應該能更確實的邁向勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下我們的計劃\N也能更順利的發展下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.86,0:02:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張金卡代表著\N我們對妳的感謝之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「嘆息的玫瑰唸珠」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然身體上沒有任何異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因為精神上極度疲勞\N還是請各位晚一點再會面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問妳喔蒂卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓莉露小姐獨處不會有問題吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不用擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她馬上就會恢復吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露窺視到了外星異種的"記憶"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那些情報量太大\N所以才會產生精神錯亂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文是這麼告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種(傑拉拜亞)的記憶是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是雷文還是桑德曼\N一定還有些什麼重要的事瞞著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們找各位找了好久\N少爺、小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐她不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.84,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天一大早就沒看到她\N結果到她房間一看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桌上只留下了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我突然不告而別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來隸屬的單位\N正是EFA的情報部...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說吧\N我就是EFA派來的間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了盜取超重神的機密資料\N才隱瞞身份潛入城內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要EFA戰力能增強的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和外星異種的戰爭\N也就能結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然相處時間很短\N不論如何我都很感謝各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了...\N和你們在一起我很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定有什麼地方搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼他們有下達什麼指示嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N他們說沒有必要去追她回來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該早就通通知道了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是莉露的事...\N就連綾香的事也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼重要的事都瞞著我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暗中拿我們逗樂子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生才不會是那樣子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.58,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我真是太不知分寸了\N我...我怎麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都明白的蝶雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐總是那麼堅強\N也是我們大家所憧憬的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(北之塔的密碼...幫我問候綾香喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湛藍的海恬靜的海濱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的...好安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來媚月真的是間諜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...到現在還沒辦法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和超重皇的停機坪好像哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道這是什麼玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這種東西\N只要隨便摸它個兩下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在玩什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會是什麼難道你...哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是立體虛擬影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會有身在水中的感覺\N但還是能呼吸和說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為這下死定了呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好險...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是哪裡的海中映像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡的...會是哪兒呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼了?發生什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城市被...太悽慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡...難道是...地球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是...並不是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(本日破曉前)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(傑拉拜亞大量殺戮機系統)\N(自衛星軌道上...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在說什麼啊?\N(展開了無差別攻擊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(使得機械城市遭到了致命性損害)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好悽慘...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...海洋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.94,0:09:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭比亞斯的海洋汙染\N已經到達極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不撤離的話\N我們就只有全滅一途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭比亞斯的那些傢伙\N還想要來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.79,0:09:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們瑟力亞斯光是為了維持現狀\N就已經精疲力竭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法再接受更多移民了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們老早就逃到開拓星球\N居然還有臉對留守者見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.87,0:09:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們故意這麼晚來\N是想奪走我們辛苦建設的成果嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位請稍安勿躁\N先看看這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是桑德曼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用我們正在開發中的創星機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用超重Σ的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說是瑟力亞斯星的開發\N就連蘭比亞斯的污染也能夠終止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紙上談兵的空談就免了吧疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是連找個駕駛員都有問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉拜亞博士\N您的大舅子好像還沒認清事實嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這表示桑德曼和外星異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是從外星來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來傑拉拜亞(外星異種)\N是取自別人的名字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.98,0:10:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然桑德曼是傑拉拜亞的大舅子\N這麼說來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.38,0:10:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是莉露.傑拉拜亞的\N親戚之類的囉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼! 桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.39,0:10:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露她...是我的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.34,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭似乎...已經無法避免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到我們的創星機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到超重Σ...\N連星球都能創造的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.79,0:11:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的想法應該就會改變才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說對吧雷文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的星球正要滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了活下去只有進行屠殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那也算是正義的話那我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以完全自主行動的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制會對目標地點趕盡殺絕\N的"大量殺戮機系統"...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.04,0:11:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您真的認為有必要用這種機械嗎?\N修紀大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.88,0:11:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣蘭比亞斯數十億的生命\N將能因此得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為會自然分解\N所以也不會造成污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.12,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為此而犧牲瑟力亞斯數萬條生命\N我實在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果非得要流血的話\N還是流的越少越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼覺得嗎?疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.07,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不弄髒自己的手\N連打倒的對手有多痛都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣根本是機械才有的行為模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是人類該用的手段!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.81,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在機械外殼下又何妨\N我們非得要繼續活下去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箭也已經射出去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算硬碰硬我也要阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.35,0:12:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連一個人都救不了的你\N又還能做些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我妹妹...\N害露菲拉早死的人就是你疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果光會空談理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法營造等質結果的話\N那就一點意義也沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重Σ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創星機?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把控制裝置給...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.64,0:12:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道...\N自己現在到底做了些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不受控制的大量殺戮機系統\N將會開始失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說是瑟力亞斯了\N就連蘭比亞斯上的一切生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會被趕盡殺絕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量殺戮機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠超重神的原型機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人...人被壓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉原諒我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不應該...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不應該是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才和我分開妻子就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨著我的修紀.傑拉拜亞\N也死在瓦礫堆下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑟力亞斯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭比亞斯的所有同胞們\N也全都死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.41,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我獨自在這\N遙遠的星球上苟活著...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了時空?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.56,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據逃生艇航道\N進行自動追溯的結果判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是中途\N空間跳躍失敗的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.53,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對她的主觀時間來說\N就只是經過了數個月而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到這個新天地\N我的同胞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能活著真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人...就是莉露嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.83,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露.傑拉拜亞\N這是連她自己都忘掉的本名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.64,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會失去記憶也是能理解的\N像這種痛苦的記憶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露她...她知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.31,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不修紀.傑拉拜亞並沒有\N告訴她我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他沒讓我知道\N莉露出生的事情一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她平靜下來之後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.09,0:17:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算以父親的身份和她相認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來莉露並不是孤獨一個人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望她的精神能快點恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和外星異種的接觸\N造成了她的記憶陸續恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還處於精神不穩定的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想請諸位\N暫時先在一旁靜靜看護就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這包在我們身上吧對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今沒告訴諸位一切真相\N都怪我太懦弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今之後還希望諸位能和我\N一同繼續奮戰下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是我一廂情願的請求\N但拜託諸位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.89,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生才不會是那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.86,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你主動拜託別人...\N感覺起來還真不像你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.38,0:18:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會讓這顆星球\N也變成那樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連星球也能創造的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創星機是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.49,0:18:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很寂寞吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起打擾到你了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以到外面來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.88,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為睡在房裡的話\N就會一直做惡夢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我也想快點好起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得心裡好煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.19,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是要想起什麼似的\N卻又想不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔心著我到底遺忘了什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙這裡到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心吧莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看過這個\N妳就能明白一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼他就是你的爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅...修紀舅舅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有個會去迎接妳的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼自己也都不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.53,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼啊...\N莉露他就是你的爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂到底又怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想要讓她高興...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.74,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...你讓她看了那些東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(希望妳能把我當做妳的親人)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅你在哪裡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那傢伙沒來的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別碰她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脈搏減弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救護班快一點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道就不會\N體諒一下別人的心情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.36,0:21:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓莉露看到那些畫面\N她會怎麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.23,0:21:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不會多考慮一下嗎?\N你這個機械混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.28,0:22:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.89,0:22:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.99,0:22:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.74,0:22:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.78,0:22:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.95,0:22:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.53,0:22:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.06,0:22:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.20,0:22:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.97,0:23:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.15,0:23:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.25,0:23:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.32,0:23:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神的秘密終於揭開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.34,0:23:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這只是一場重大悲劇\N的序幕而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺\N請您打起精神來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.08,0:23:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家...愛娜不論發生什麼事\N都會一直陪伴在您身旁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入沈睡中的莉露\N掉進悲慟之中的桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.88,0:23:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.89,0:23:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警終於揭開面紗\N展露出駭人威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回「粉碎的女神(機組)」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.59,0:23:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會守護住斗牙少爺的!